Cyberpunk style: A glowing holographic blueprint floating in a dark neon-lit workspace, showing interconnected geometric cubes and hexagonal nodes representing data structures. The cubes pulse with electric blue and magenta energy, connected by flowing streams of luminescent data particles. In the foreground, translucent crystalline containers morph and reshape themselves, symbolizing data transformation. The scene is bathed in deep purple shadows with cyan accent lighting, rain-streaked windows visible in the background reflecting the digital glow. Circuit-board patterns subtly embedded in the reflective floor surface.
